stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> NavigateToTrafficFilters
    NavigateToTrafficFilters --> FetchFilters : GET /api/alerts/traffic-filters/
    FetchFilters --> DisplayFilterList
    DisplayFilterList --> ClickNewRule
    ClickNewRule --> SelectCategory : volume/login/domain/custom
    SelectCategory --> SelectFilterType : ip_range/port/protocol
    SelectFilterType --> EnterValue
    EnterValue --> SetThreshold : count + window
    SetThreshold --> SelectAction : suppress/highlight/block
    SelectAction --> CreateRule : POST /api/alerts/traffic-filters/
    CreateRule --> RuleCreated
    RuleCreated --> DisplayFilterList
    DisplayFilterList --> ToggleRule : Enable/Disable
    DisplayFilterList --> DeleteRule
    DisplayFilterList --> [*]